2020 Acquisitions 

&#8203; 

During the year ended December 31, 2020, the Company completed two acquisitions for $ 50.4 , net of cash acquired. One of the acquisitions was included in the Harsh Environment Solutions segment, and the other acquisition was included in the Interconnect and Sensor Systems segment. The Company completed the acquisition accounting, including the analyses of the fair value of the assets acquired and liabilities assumed, for both 2020 acquisitions, and the final assessments of values did not differ materially from the previous preliminary assessments. Pro forma financial information, as well as further details regarding the purchase price allocation related to these acquisitions, was not presented, since these acquisitions were not material, either individually or in the aggregate, to the Company&#8217;s financial results. 

